ZH: 这里有三艘渔船停在海边。
EN: There are three fishing boats moored at the shore.

ZH: 我们租了一艘帆船去岛上的海域探险。
EN: We rented a sailboat to explore the waters around the island.

ZH: 那艘巨型货轮装载着成千上万的集装箱。
EN: That massive cargo ship is loaded with thousands of shipping containers.

ZH: 昨天去码头看到一艘漂亮的游艇。
EN: I saw a beautiful yacht at the pier yesterday.

ZH: 手里也许会有一艘小船来接我们。
EN: Perhaps there will be a small boat to pick us up.

ZH: 救援队已经派出一艘船去搜寻失踪的渔民。
EN: The rescue team has dispatched a boat to search for the missing fishermen.

ZH: 外面有一艘游船售票处。
EN: There is a ticket booth for a sightseeing boat outside.

ZH: 这是张给你的邀请函，要求你加入我们的那艘航空母舰。
EN: This is an invitation for you to join us on our aircraft carrier.

ZH: 我很羡慕那艘前来拯救我们的船只。
EN: I am envious of the ship that has come to save us.

ZH: ZH: 他们用了一艘小船到达了两岸之间的小岛。
EN: They used a small boat to reach the island between the two shores.

ZH: 老板正在考虑购买另一艘游艇进行投资。
EN: The boss is considering buying another yacht for investment.

ZH: 他们需要一艘大型船只来运送国际货物。
EN: They need a large vessel to transport international goods.

ZH: 我们将会坐上那艘邮轮开始我们的海上之旅。
EN: We will board the cruise ship to start our journey at sea.

ZH: 那个海盗团队驶向了一艘在太平洋航行的货船。
EN: The pirate crew set sail towards a cargo ship traveling in the Pacific Ocean.

ZH: 观看者的目光聚集在了一艘正在进行对决的赛船上。
EN: The spectators' attention was focused on a racing boat competing in a match.

ZH: 团队计划使用一艘潜艇来进行海底勘探。
EN: The team plans to use a submarine for underwater exploration.

ZH: 那艘破船因为海难而搁浅在了海岸旁。
EN: The broken ship ran aground by the coast due to a maritime accident.

ZH: 提前准备好一艘大巴士来接我们的团队。
EN: Have a coach ready to pick up our team in advance.

ZH: 那艘护卫舰扬起了船旗以示庆祝。
EN: The escort ship raised the flag to celebrate.

ZH: 检查一下这艘帆船的船体是否有损坏。
